name: nionswift-instrumentation
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "nionswift-instrumentation" %}
{% set version = "0.20.7" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0f2acb25d91a155c66f07d9c39a623da259fd0f6499322e06305f6d3e1445824

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.8
  run:
    - niondata >=0.14.0,<0.16.0
    - nionswift >=0.16.0,<0.17.0
    - nionui >=0.6.3,<0.7.0
    - nionutils >=0.4.1,<0.5.0
    - python >=3.8
    - numpy >=1.21,<2.0

test:
  imports:
    - nion.instrumentation
    - nion.instrumentation.test
    - nionswift_plugin.nion_instrumentation_ui

about:
  home: https://nionswift-instrumentation.readthedocs.io
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A Nion Swift library for STEM instrumentation (Camera, Scan, Video, Microscope).
  doc_url: https://nionswift-instrumentation.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/nion-software/nionswift-instrumentation-kit

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cmeyer
    - nion-gwyn
